      "content": "it's not even about small steps anymore. that's the problem. i've tried every \"small step\" and every \"coping mechanism\" out there. it feels less like a bug and more like a design flaw. like i'm built to just fail over and over. there's no patch for this. no matter what i do, the loop just resets.",
